i need a sentence for impetus please in physics the law of inertia says that an object at rest tends to stay at rest until moved upon by an outside force when an outside force is applied to an object at rest it gives the object the impetus or the initial energy necessary to start it moving we also apply this same concept to people if we avoid doing things we sometimes need an outside force to help us change for example my father's death from lung cancer was the impetus my brother needed to quit smoking hope this helps Irreducible complexity CPU cache Charades Intelligent design Xenomorph Password (game) Calvin and Hobbes Lingo (game show) Wheel of Fortune Milton H. Erickson Miss Saigon House of M Captain Marvel (DC Comics) Ellipsis Supergirl Password cracking Bible code Yoga Sutras of Patanjali Wild Wild West Mostly Harmless Chain Reaction (game show) Ric Flair Harp Theory Mental illness Cranium (board game) Lottie Dod Time travel Special relativity The Wizard of Oz (1939 film) The Tenth Planet Acts of the Apostles Amy Dumas Guess Who's Coming to Criticize Dinner? Scrabble (game show) Voynich manuscript Artificial consciousness Terraforming Libertarian socialism Hangman News style Brave New World Inch Luminiferous aether Santa Anita Handicap Tide Quantum mechanics Bad Wolf Discordianism Philosophy of space and time Totally bounded space Bigfoot USB flash drive Lipogram Left-handed G-Man (Half-Life) Sicilian language I'm Sorry I Haven't a Clue American Sign Language Do the Handicapped Go To Hell?/Probably Password Dactyly Dog Vacuum The Goon Show Creation-evolution controversy Cool (African philosophy) Professor X STS-114 Dark matter Crossword General Grievous Bing Crosby Never Mind The Buzzcocks Old Tongue Bah__'__ Faith and Science Recurrence relation Speech synthesis SMTV Live The Hobbit Jean Grey Tambourine Saudade Go (board game) Pictionary Postmodernity Liaison The Doctor Dances Classified information Mouse (computing) M-theory Pyramid (game show) Plurality ele